title: No Mercy - Greatest Hits (2007) APE
description: No Mercy - Greatest Hits (2007) APE No Mercy is a trio of American singers who were originally brought together in Germany by producer Frank Farian. The group consists of Bronx-born Marty Cintron and twin brothers Ariel and Gabriel Hernández, who hailed from Miami. This is a collection of the finest tracks from this soulful and romantic R&B/Electronic trio. If you have a taste for the Farian-esque, this album is for you.
